                  "text": "Ya what's zey want?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Grimesquit",
                  "text": "I don't know it's why I is asking 'em."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Phingspet",
                  "text": "Why do we care what zey wants let's get back to rat splattin'."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Grimesquit",
                  "text": "Ya good plan."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Em... Ahemm.. Excuse me?"
