        },
        {
          "title": "After the completion of Ratcatchers",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Grimesquit",
                  "text": "Eh? Would you credit da."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Phingspet",
                  "text": "Wha?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Grimesquit",
                  "text": "It's [player name] again init?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Phingspet",
                  "text": "Wha?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Grimesquit",
                  "text": "[player name] has come back again."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Phingspet",
                  "text": "S' wha does 'ey want?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Oh come on, stop the act. It's just not funny anymore."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Grimesquit",
                  "text": "Ya it is."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Phingspet",
                  "text": "Ha! Ha!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Grimesquit",
                  "text": "Ha! Ha!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Can you tell me where I would find Jimmy Dazzler?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Grimesquit",
                  "text": "'Ees in Ardougne. In ee?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Phingspet",
                  "text": "'e is, e is. He stays in the Flying Horse dun 'e?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Grimesquit",
                  "text": "Tell 'im we said 'ello. Will ye? She then breaks out in a burst of girly giggles."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Can you tell me where I would find Hooknosed Jack?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Grimesquit",
                  "text": "Da big ugly's ere in Vu'rock."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Phingspet",
                  "text": "Da big ugly! Ha that's a good one. 'E is big n ugly though isn't e, serve him right for all the fights e get's in."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Grimesquit",
                  "text": "Ha! I nose the truth when I 'ears it! Get it? Get it? Nose the truth?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Phingspet",
                  "text": "Ha, ha, ha ah ha....."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Can you tell me where I would find Smokin' Joe?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Grimesquit",
                  "text": "Short stuff's out in Keldagrime."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Can you tell me where I would find the Face?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Grimesquit",
                  "text": "Hey features? Where is she?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Phingspet",
                  "text": "Port Sarim last I 'eard."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Can you tell me where I would find Felkrash?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Grimesquit",
                  "text": "She's travels about a bit, but I reckon Port Sarim."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
